{"tid":750851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「學生獨立聯盟」參與民陣遊行　聲援民族黨陳浩天","createTime":"2018-07-21T10:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T07:21:09.000Z","uid":47359,"like":18,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"20f1948ded13362f609fc17f8d91605a3454b12c","tid":750851,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:21:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1408195-20180721.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1408195-20180721.htm&d=%2FGrfE0Fn325czZ%2FxUEZaLf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=a9e0f399\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1408195-20180721.htm&h=098a5a15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1408195-20180721.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n「學生獨立聯盟」參與民陣遊行　聲援民族黨陳浩天<br />\n2018-07-21 HKT 15:22<br />\n 分享工具\t facebook  twitter<br />\n 遊行人士高舉抗議標語。（仇志榮攝）<br />\n遊行人士高舉抗議標語。（仇志榮攝）<br />\n民陣下午發起遊行，抗議當局計劃禁止主張港獨的香港民族黨繼續運作。主張港獨的「學生獨立聯盟」亦有參與遊行，指要聲援民族黨召集人陳浩天。<br />\n<br />\n20多名聯盟成員在灣仔修頓球場集合，他們高舉「香港獨立」的旗幟，有人舉起「只有兩國，才有兩制」、「香港唔獨、實變大陸」的標語，部分人戴上帽和口罩。<br />\n<br />\n聯盟發言人呂俊賢說，不滿和不能接受當局打壓香港民族黨，相信是一個警號，當局將來會打擊聯盟和泛民政黨，他說成立組織時已預計被打壓，不存在擔心的問題，強調絕對不會調整綱領和行動，亦有準備承擔入獄的風險。"},{"pid":"5cc9deb79aa12a1c17c1fcf8f29bf14e83f6a906","tid":750851,"uid":47359,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8baa0489972c9aac5a32d836d628ad0db3b3e464","tid":750851,"uid":176366,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f794ce92a86fb8d7ed4dc19f9886b89e49e9802b","tid":750851,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:23:34.000Z","msg":"吊那星 有20人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 