1,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"442730cc16a3233752af43f7410f0f48e0207c40","tid":750851,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd59d7e2233bed507e828ecb17e720e3dfc0d864","tid":750851,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"717fad8d687231fb5b29a09e4fe03b78ac22b8cf","tid":750851,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:42:34.000Z","msg":"五毛戚繼光<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/21/184232_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F21%2F184232_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=383cf4c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e14315555a39ca081873a571a19c96c9604ae7ef","tid":750851,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5278ceae8d7cd486d512dd89067da769984aa01","tid":750851,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:45:36.000Z","msg":"民陣發起遊行反對禁止民族黨運作<br />\n民陣發起遊行，反對警方引用《社團條例》禁止民族黨運作，有支持港獨的團體參與，民陣指各團體有不同政治主張，但都有一個共通點，就是捍衛基本法保障的言論及結社自由，又指遊行有一千二百人參與，警方就估計最高峰時有六百人。<br />\n<br />\n遊行隊伍下午三時由灣仔修頓球場外出發，部份人沿途吹哨子，批評警方以《社團條例》扼殺市民結社自由，如同吹黑哨。參與遊行的有民主派政黨、本土派團體，亦有多個主張港獨的組織在隊尾加入遊行，舉起港獨旗幟。遊行隊伍去到軒尼詩道的時候，遇到支持取締民族黨的保衛香港運動離遠抗議，他們最後去到警察總部集會，不同團體先後上台發言。<br />\n<br />\n遊行人士擔心今次會開先例，未來政府有機會再用《社團條例》取締不同政見的團體，民陣向警方遞交請願信後結束集會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/531313\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F531313&d=%2FGrfE0Fn325czZ%2FxUEZaLf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=d1d5f8f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F531313&h=7020dddf\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/531313</a><br />\n<br />\n有線嘅報道"},{"pid":"cb8753bfef4f7c7b6cea6b294b9911b2e02f8953","tid":750851,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d5278ceae8d7cd486d512dd89067da769984aa01","tid":750851,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:45:36.000Z","msg":"民陣發起遊行反對禁止民族黨運作<br />\n民陣發起遊行，反對警方引用《社團條例》禁止民族黨運作，有支持港獨的團體參與，民陣指各團體有不同政治主張，但都有一個共通點，就是捍衛基本法保障的言論及結社自由，又指遊行有一千二百人參與，警方就估計最高峰時有六百人。<br />\n<br />\n遊行隊伍下午三時由灣仔修頓球場外出發，部份人沿途吹哨子，批評警方以《社團條例》扼殺市民結社自由，如同吹黑哨。參與遊行的有民主派政黨、本土派團體，亦有多個主張港獨的組織在隊尾加入遊行，舉起港獨旗幟。遊行隊伍去到軒尼詩道的時候，遇到支持取締民族黨的保衛香港運動離遠抗議，他們最後去到警察總部集會，不同團體先後上台發言。<br />\n<br />\n遊行人士擔心今次會開先例，未來政府有機會再用《社團條例》取締不同政見的團體，民陣向警方遞交請願信後結束集會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/531313\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F531313&d=%2FGrfE0Fn325czZ%2FxUEZaLf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=d1d5f8f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F531313&h=7020dddf\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/531313</a><br />\n<br />\n有線嘅報道"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6691211479f838513092110cee5b715f3da8921","tid":750851,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}